===margin===
边距
;<code>margin=0px</code>
===parent===
母专题
;<code>parent=</code>
:Name of parent WikiProject, e.g., for Wikipedia:WikiProject South America use {{para|parent|South America}}. Providing this adds <code>"and/or the parent project"</code> to the "why not join" message. Only works if status is <code>inactive</code> or <code>defunct</code>.
===type===
类型
;<code>type=</code>
:Choose from: <code>anime and manga</code>, <code>band</code>, <code>edu</code>, <code>game</code>, <code>geo</code>, <code>sports</code>, or <code>TV show</code>; presently this feature is only used for subcategorization of WikiProjects in media, fandom, and youth subculture subject areas, as well as geographic subject areas. This is because those subject areas attract the creation of numerous narrowly topical projects.
===mergedto===
合并
;<code>mergedto=</code>
:Indicates the target of a merge, ''merged to WikiProject <var>Foo</var>''.  This parameter's value is the name of the wikiproject without the "Wikipedia:WikiProject" part.
===date===
日期
;<code>date=</code>
:用于记录该专题被标注为半活跃，不活跃或废弃专题的日期。

===note===
注释
;<code>note=</code>
:设置将在横幅中出现的注释。
===portal===
专题
;<code>portal=</code>
:添加一个到关联[[WP:Portal|主题]]页面的链接。例如，对于主题：美国请使用{{para|portal|美国}}

===Shortcut paramenters===
快捷参数
;<code>sc1=WP:快捷方式1</code>
;<code>sc2=WP:快捷方式2</code>
;<code>sc3=WP:快捷方式3</code>
;<code>sc4=WP:快捷方式4</code>
;<code>sc5=WP:快捷方式5</code>

===nocat===
不分类
;<code>nocat=</code>
:如果将其设置为<code>true</code>，则不会加入分类。
===Task forces===
工作组<br />
在[[Wikipedia:专题委员会/专题指引/工作组|工作组]]（即子项目）页面上使用时进行设置。仅在状态设置为<code>active</code>时有效
;<code>taskforce=yes</code>
;<code>project-type=</code>
:设置为<code>topic</code>或<code>process</code>, then complete in the matching parameter
;<code>topic=</code>
:Use this for task forces working on a particular topic within a WikiProject
;<code>process=</code>
:Use this for task forces working on improvement of a particular process within a WikiProject

